data.description: Large split-level brick house on great corner lot. 3 bedrooms/2 full bathrooms. Beautiful kitchen with Quartz countertops and Stainless Steel appliances. Living room/Dining combo has brand new White Oak hardwood flooring. Full second bath and great Family Room on lower level. Brand new windows and water heater. Well-maintained HVAC. Roof 2015. Ready to move in. Great Location, close to everything, and ready to be your new home!
